title: Nathan Seaway
text:
Hello! Welcome to my personal website. My name is Nathan Seaway, and I am a fourth year student at UCSB, majoring in Environmental Studies with a minor in French. This website showcases some of my hobbies, projects, and work experiences. Thank you for visiting!
